Why join Societe Generale Group?

   Being part of the workforce at Societe Generale, means joining a Group
   that looks to the future with optimism and determination in a complex
   macro-economic environment. You will enter a company that is striving -
   alongside students, citizens and entrepreneurs - to create a better
   world; a company with fierce entrepreneurial spirit and which is
   determined to be the most innovative among French banks.
